snippet.title: Monster Prom 4: Monster Con - Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
"Monster Prom 4: Monster Con" is coming out this April 24th!

Wishlist the game - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2869860/Monster_Prom_4_Monster_Con/

Discord: https://discord.com/invite/monsterprom 
Twitter: https://x.com/monsterprom  
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/btflglitch/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@btflglitch/

Can you find love at the wildest nerd convention ever? 
"Monster Con" goes back to the multiplayer dating sim formula: go through absurd and funny situations as you find love among six sexy monsters!

Who will you romance? The mimic who cosplays? The idol clown? Or everyone's favorite eldritch cutie? (there's also Liam)
